('KIT_WIZARD', 'equipment', 'Kit, Wizard', '0', NULL, '1.2', NULL, '2.2', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'If you want to quickly decide how to spend your starting money on what your class needs, start with one of these kits. Note than an adventurer’s pack, which is included in each kit, contains a backpack, a bedroll, two belt pouches, 10 pieces of chalk, flint and steel, 50 feet of rope, 2 weeks’ rations, soap, 5 torches, and a waterskin.<br>Weapons staff<br>Gear adventurer''s pack, material component pouch, writing set', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Rules.aspx?ID=240'),
('ALCHEMIST_S_LAB', 'equipment', 'Alchemist''s Lab', '0', NULL, '5', '2', '6', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'You need an alchemist’s lab to Craft alchemical items during downtime.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=2'),
('THUNDERSTONE_LESSER)', 'alchemical', 'Thunderstone (Lesser)', '1', NULL, '3', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When this stone hits a creature or a hard surface, it explodes with a deafening bang. A thunderstone deals the listed sonic damage and sonic splash damage, and each creature within 10 feet of the space in which the stone exploded must succeed at a Fortitude saving throw with the listed DC or be deafened until the end of its next turn. Many types of thunderstone grant an item bonus to attack rolls. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bomb deals 1d4 sonic damage and 1 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 17.<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d4 sonic damage and 2 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 20.<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d4 sonic damage and 3 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 28.<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d4 sonic damage and 4 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 36.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=79'),
('FROST_VIAL_MAJOR)', 'alchemical', 'Frost Vial (Major)', '17', NULL, '2500', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The liquid reagents in this vial rapidly absorb heat when exposed to air. A frost vial deals the listed cold damage and cold splash damage. On a hit, the target takes a status penalty to its Speeds until the end of its next&nbsp;turn. Many types of frost vial also grant an item bonus to attack rolls.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bomb deals 1d6 cold damage and 1 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –5-foot penalty.<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls, the bomb deals 2d6 cold damage and 2 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –10-foot penalty.<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls, the bomb deals 3d6 cold damage and 3 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –10-foot penalty.<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls, the bomb deals 4d6 cold damage and 4 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –15-foot penalty.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=77'),
('BOTTLED_LIGHTNING_LESSER)', 'alchemical', 'Bottled Lightning (Lesser)', '1', NULL, '3', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bottled lightning is packed with volatile reagents that create a blast of electricity when they are exposed to air. Bottled lightning deals the listed electricity damage and electricity splash damage. On a hit, the target becomes flat-footed until the start of your next turn. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>It deals 1d6 electricity damage and 1 electricity splash damage.<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d6 electricity damage and 2 electricity splash damage.<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d6 electricity damage and 3 electricity splash damage.<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d6 electricity damage and 4 electricity splash damage.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=76'),
('TANGLEFOOT_BAG_LESSER)', 'alchemical', 'Tanglefoot Bag (Lesser)', '1', NULL, '3', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A tanglefoot bag is filled with sticky substances. When you hit a creature with a tanglefoot bag, that creature takes a status penalty to its Speeds for 1 minute. Many types of tanglefoot bag also grant an item bonus on attack rolls.<br><br> On a critical hit, a creature in contact with a solid surface becomes stuck to the surface and immobilized for 1 round, and a creature flying via wings has its wings tangled, causing it to fall safely to the ground and become unable to Fly again for 1 round. Tanglefoot bags are not effective when used on a creature that is in water.<br><br> The target can end any effects by Escaping or spending a total of 3 Interact actions to carefully remove the sticky substances. These Interact actions don’t have to be consecutive, and other creatures can provide the actions as well.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Tanglefoot Bag (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The target takes a –10-foot penalty, and the Escape DC is 17.<br><br><b>Tanglefoot Bag (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls, the target takes a –15-foot penalty, and the Escape DC is 19.<br><br><b>Tanglefoot Bag (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls, the target takes a –15-foot penalty, and the Escape DC is 28.<br><br><b>Tanglefoot Bag (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls, the target takes a –20-foot penalty, and the Escape DC is 37.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=78'),
('ACID_FLASK_GREATER)', 'alchemical', 'Acid Flask (Greater)', '11', NULL, '250', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This flask filled with corrosive acid deals 1 acid damage, the listed persistent acid damage, and the listed acid splash damage. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>It deals 1d6 persistent acid damage and 1 acid splash damage.<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d6 persistent acid damage and 2 acid splash damage.<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d6 persistent acid damage and 3 acid splash damage.<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d6 persistent acid damage and 4 acid splash damage.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=74'),
('BOTTLED_LIGHTNING_MAJOR)', 'alchemical', 'Bottled Lightning (Major)', '17', NULL, '2500', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bottled lightning is packed with volatile reagents that create a blast of electricity when they are exposed to air. Bottled lightning deals the listed electricity damage and electricity splash damage. On a hit, the target becomes flat-footed until the start of your next turn. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>It deals 1d6 electricity damage and 1 electricity splash damage.<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d6 electricity damage and 2 electricity splash damage.<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d6 electricity damage and 3 electricity splash damage.<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d6 electricity damage and 4 electricity splash damage.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=76'),
('BOTTLED_LIGHTNING_GREATER)', 'alchemical', 'Bottled Lightning (Greater)', '11', NULL, '250', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Bottled lightning is packed with volatile reagents that create a blast of electricity when they are exposed to air. Bottled lightning deals the listed electricity damage and electricity splash damage. On a hit, the target becomes flat-footed until the start of your next turn. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>It deals 1d6 electricity damage and 1 electricity splash damage.<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d6 electricity damage and 2 electricity splash damage.<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d6 electricity damage and 3 electricity splash damage.<br><br><b>Bottled Lightning (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d6 electricity damage and 4 electricity splash damage.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=76'),
('ACID_FLASK_MODERATE)', 'alchemical', 'Acid Flask (Moderate)', '3', NULL, '10', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This flask filled with corrosive acid deals 1 acid damage, the listed persistent acid damage, and the listed acid splash damage. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>It deals 1d6 persistent acid damage and 1 acid splash damage.<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d6 persistent acid damage and 2 acid splash damage.<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d6 persistent acid damage and 3 acid splash damage.<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d6 persistent acid damage and 4 acid splash damage.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=74'),
('ALCHEMIST_S_FIRE_GREATER)', 'alchemical', 'Alchemist''s Fire (Greater)', '11', NULL, '250', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Alchemist’s fire is a combination of volatile liquids that ignite when exposed to air. Alchemist’s fire deals the listed fire damage, persistent fire damage, and splash damage. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bomb deals 1d8 fire damage, 1 persistent fire damage, and 1 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d8 fire damage, 2 persistent fire damage, and 2 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d8 fire damage, 3 persistent fire damage, and 3 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d8 fire damage, 4 persistent fire damage, and 4 fire splash damage.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=75'),
('ACID_FLASK_LESSER)', 'alchemical', 'Acid Flask (Lesser)', '1', NULL, '3', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'This flask filled with corrosive acid deals 1 acid damage, the listed persistent acid damage, and the listed acid splash damage. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>It deals 1d6 persistent acid damage and 1 acid splash damage.<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d6 persistent acid damage and 2 acid splash damage.<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d6 persistent acid damage and 3 acid splash damage.<br><br><b>Acid Flask (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d6 persistent acid damage and 4 acid splash damage.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=74'),
('ALCHEMIST_S_FIRE_MODERATE)', 'alchemical', 'Alchemist''s Fire (Moderate)', '3', NULL, '10', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Alchemist’s fire is a combination of volatile liquids that ignite when exposed to air. Alchemist’s fire deals the listed fire damage, persistent fire damage, and splash damage. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bomb deals 1d8 fire damage, 1 persistent fire damage, and 1 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d8 fire damage, 2 persistent fire damage, and 2 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d8 fire damage, 3 persistent fire damage, and 3 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d8 fire damage, 4 persistent fire damage, and 4 fire splash damage.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=75'),
('FROST_VIAL_MODERATE)', 'alchemical', 'Frost Vial (Moderate)', '3', NULL, '10', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The liquid reagents in this vial rapidly absorb heat when exposed to air. A frost vial deals the listed cold damage and cold splash damage. On a hit, the target takes a status penalty to its Speeds until the end of its next&nbsp;turn. Many types of frost vial also grant an item bonus to attack rolls.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bomb deals 1d6 cold damage and 1 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –5-foot penalty.<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls, the bomb deals 2d6 cold damage and 2 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –10-foot penalty.<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls, the bomb deals 3d6 cold damage and 3 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –10-foot penalty.<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls, the bomb deals 4d6 cold damage and 4 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –15-foot penalty.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=77'),
('THUNDERSTONE_MODERATE)', 'alchemical', 'Thunderstone (Moderate)', '3', NULL, '10', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When this stone hits a creature or a hard surface, it explodes with a deafening bang. A thunderstone deals the listed sonic damage and sonic splash damage, and each creature within 10 feet of the space in which the stone exploded must succeed at a Fortitude saving throw with the listed DC or be deafened until the end of its next turn. Many types of thunderstone grant an item bonus to attack rolls. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bomb deals 1d4 sonic damage and 1 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 17.<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d4 sonic damage and 2 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 20.<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d4 sonic damage and 3 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 28.<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d4 sonic damage and 4 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 36.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=79'),
('THUNDERSTONE_GREATER)', 'alchemical', 'Thunderstone (Greater)', '11', NULL, '250', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'When this stone hits a creature or a hard surface, it explodes with a deafening bang. A thunderstone deals the listed sonic damage and sonic splash damage, and each creature within 10 feet of the space in which the stone exploded must succeed at a Fortitude saving throw with the listed DC or be deafened until the end of its next turn. Many types of thunderstone grant an item bonus to attack rolls. <br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bomb deals 1d4 sonic damage and 1 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 17.<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d4 sonic damage and 2 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 20.<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d4 sonic damage and 3 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 28.<br><br><b>Thunderstone (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d4 sonic damage and 4 sonic splash damage, and the DC is 36.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=79'),
('ALCHEMIST_S_FIRE_MAJOR)', 'alchemical', 'Alchemist''s Fire (Major)', '17', NULL, '2500', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Alchemist’s fire is a combination of volatile liquids that ignite when exposed to air. Alchemist’s fire deals the listed fire damage, persistent fire damage, and splash damage. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bomb deals 1d8 fire damage, 1 persistent fire damage, and 1 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d8 fire damage, 2 persistent fire damage, and 2 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d8 fire damage, 3 persistent fire damage, and 3 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d8 fire damage, 4 persistent fire damage, and 4 fire splash damage.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=75'),
('FROST_VIAL_GREATER)', 'alchemical', 'Frost Vial (Greater)', '11', NULL, '250', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The liquid reagents in this vial rapidly absorb heat when exposed to air. A frost vial deals the listed cold damage and cold splash damage. On a hit, the target takes a status penalty to its Speeds until the end of its next&nbsp;turn. Many types of frost vial also grant an item bonus to attack rolls.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bomb deals 1d6 cold damage and 1 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –5-foot penalty.<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls, the bomb deals 2d6 cold damage and 2 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –10-foot penalty.<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls, the bomb deals 3d6 cold damage and 3 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –10-foot penalty.<br><br><b>Frost Vial (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls, the bomb deals 4d6 cold damage and 4 cold splash damage, and the target takes a –15-foot penalty.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=77'),
('TANGLEFOOT_BAG_MAJOR)', 'alchemical', 'Tanglefoot Bag (Major)', '17', NULL, '2500', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A tanglefoot bag is filled with sticky substances. When you hit a creature with a tanglefoot bag, that creature takes a status penalty to its Speeds for 1 minute. Many types of tanglefoot bag also grant an item bonus on attack rolls.<br><br> On a critical hit, a creature in contact with a solid surface becomes stuck to the surface and immobilized for 1 round, and a creature flying via wings has its wings tangled, causing it to fall safely to the ground and become unable to Fly again for 1 round. Tanglefoot bags are not effective when used on a creature that is in water.<br><br> The target can end any effects by Escaping or spending a total of 3 Interact actions to carefully remove the sticky substances. These Interact actions don’t have to be consecutive, and other creatures can provide the actions as well.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Tanglefoot Bag (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The target takes a –10-foot penalty, and the Escape DC is 17.<br><br><b>Tanglefoot Bag (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls, the target takes a –15-foot penalty, and the Escape DC is 19.<br><br><b>Tanglefoot Bag (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls, the target takes a –15-foot penalty, and the Escape DC is 28.<br><br><b>Tanglefoot Bag (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls, the target takes a –20-foot penalty, and the Escape DC is 37.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=78'),
('ALCHEMIST_S_FIRE_LESSER)', 'alchemical', 'Alchemist''s Fire (Lesser)', '1', NULL, '3', NULL, 'L', NULL, 'held in 1 hand', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Alchemist’s fire is a combination of volatile liquids that ignite when exposed to air. Alchemist’s fire deals the listed fire damage, persistent fire damage, and splash damage. Many types grant an item bonus to attack rolls.<br><br><b>Activate</b>  Strike<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Lesser) Item 1</b><br><b>Level</b> 1; <b>Price</b> 3 gp<br>The bomb deals 1d8 fire damage, 1 persistent fire damage, and 1 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Moderate) Item 3</b><br><b>Level</b> 3; <b>Price</b> 10 gp<br>You gain a +1 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 2d8 fire damage, 2 persistent fire damage, and 2 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Greater) Item 11</b><br><b>Level</b> 11; <b>Price</b> 250 gp<br>You gain a +2 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 3d8 fire damage, 3 persistent fire damage, and 3 fire splash damage.<br><br><b>Alchemist''s Fire (Major) Item 17</b><br><b>Level</b> 17; <b>Price</b> 2,500 gp<br>You gain a +3 item bonus to attack rolls. The bomb deals 4d8 fire damage, 4 persistent fire damage, and 4 fire splash damage.', NULL, 'https://2e.aonprd.com/Equipment.aspx?ID=75'),
